      "uco-core:description": "Five-day jury trial before Judge Jon Phipps McCalla in Memphis. Twelve jurors and two alternates sworn 2024-03-26; government witnesses included Jenny Chung, Olivia Johnson, Leslie Jones, Brandon Thomas, case agent Janelle Hosafros, and Derricka Harwell, with Exhibits 1-38; both defendants elected not to testify; Rule 29 motions denied. Source: PACER docket, minute entries 114, 116, 121, 126, 127",
